snippet.title: Sol Hemochroma - Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming September 4, 2018 :: An Aether Interactive production :: http://aether.in.net

An adaptation of the lost, 1980s classic film (that could've been): an enticing, alchemical conspiracy in the Canadian steeltown. Four teenagers confront the basement sickness of the town manor: and their leader seems so different, so driven, suddenly...
